Whenever you tap a permanent for mana, add {G}{G}. Spend this mana only to cast Equipment spells or to activate equip abilities.

Ward {3}
[i]Portal Testing [/i]— At the beginning of your end step, exile up to one other creature you control, then return it to the battlefield.
[i]Specimen Disposal[/i] — Whenever a creature you control enters from exile, you may sacrifice it. If you do, draw a card.

